chart.title: COVID-19 vaccine doses administered by manufacturer
chart.subtitle: All doses, including boosters, are counted individually.
chart.citation: Official data collated by Our World in Data (2024)

COVID-19 doses (cumulative) - Manufactur.descriptionShort: Total number of Pfizer/BioNTech COVID-19 vaccination doses administered.
descriptionKey: During the COVID-19 pandemic, there were various manufacturers providing vaccines. This indicator counts those doses by Pfizer/BioNTech.
Differences in vaccine availability, distribution agreements, and production capacity mean that some manufacturers' vaccines may be more widely used in specific regions.
Data on doses administered by manufacturer may be incomplete due to varied reporting standards, data sharing agreements, or privacy considerations.
COVID-19 doses (cumulative) - Manufactur.citationShort: Official data collated by Our World in Data (2024) – with major processing by Our World in Data
COVID-19 doses (cumulative) - Manufactur.citationLong: Official data collated by Our World in Data (2024) – with major processing by Our World in Data. “Pfizer/BioNTech” [dataset]. Official data collated by Our World in Data, “COVID-19, vaccinations (broken down by manufacturer)” [original data].
